  <title>Enable Last.fm scrobbling</title>

  <p>You can enable Last.fm scrobbling. You can learn more about Last.fm and scrobbling <link href="https://cbsi.secure.force.com/lastfm/articles/LastFM/What-is-scrobbling?template=template_lastfm">here</link></p>

  <steps>
    <title>In <em>GNOME Settings</em>:</title>
    <item>
      <p>Go to the <em>Online Accounts</em> tab</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Select <em>Last.fm</em></p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Enter your credentials and make sure the checkbox against <em>Music</em> is checked</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

